[
    {
        "text": "These are the faces of black soldiers during the American Civil War.",
        "startTime": 1045,
        "endTime": 5261,
        "slowStartTime": 1717,
        "slowEndTime": 8117
    },
    {
        "text": "They're rare photographs of some of the 200,000...",
        "startTime": 5699,
        "endTime": 9311,
        "slowStartTime": 8699,
        "slowEndTime": 14191
    },
    {
        "text": "...who fought in the Union army against the southern Confederacy.",
        "startTime": 9406,
        "endTime": 12906,
        "slowStartTime": 14259,
        "slowEndTime": 19584
    },
    {
        "text": "The pictures offer slices of life that many Americans may not be aware of.",
        "startTime": 13443,
        "endTime": 18691,
        "slowStartTime": 20314,
        "slowEndTime": 28261
    },
    {
        "text": "Stories like that of Adele Logan Alexander's great grandfather, John Robert Bond.",
        "startTime": 19060,
        "endTime": 25297,
        "slowStartTime": 28740,
        "slowEndTime": 38171
    },
    {
        "text": "He was born in England in 1846.",
        "startTime": 25806,
        "endTime": 29213,
        "slowStartTime": 38859,
        "slowEndTime": 44045
    },
    {
        "text": "When he was 17 years old, hearing about the struggle for Africans' freedom...",
        "startTime": 29844,
        "endTime": 35535,
        "slowStartTime": 44916,
        "slowEndTime": 53528
    },
    {
        "text": "...in the United States, the story my mother told me was that he got on a fishing boat...",
        "startTime": 36049,
        "endTime": 42723,
        "slowStartTime": 54223,
        "slowEndTime": 64309
    },
    {
        "text": "...and came to Massachusetts because he wanted to help free the slaves.",
        "startTime": 42877,
        "endTime": 50123,
        "slowStartTime": 64465,
        "slowEndTime": 75410
    },
    {
        "text": "Adele Alexander is a historian.",
        "startTime": 50487,
        "endTime": 52876,
        "slowStartTime": 75880,
        "slowEndTime": 79539
    },
    {
        "text": "She says her great grandfather joined the Union navy and was almost killed in a battle.",
        "startTime": 53375,
        "endTime": 59097,
        "slowStartTime": 80212,
        "slowEndTime": 88871
    },
    {
        "text": "It's just one of the many facts Alexander uncovered about her family.",
        "startTime": 59816,
        "endTime": 64364,
        "slowStartTime": 89874,
        "slowEndTime": 96771
    },
    {
        "text": "She says her great grandfather sacrificed to help future generations.",
        "startTime": 64817,
        "endTime": 69691,
        "slowStartTime": 97376,
        "slowEndTime": 104762
    },
    {
        "text": "Alexander says the Civil War not only freed the slaves,...",
        "startTime": 69971,
        "endTime": 73799,
        "slowStartTime": 105107,
        "slowEndTime": 110924
    },
    {
        "text": "...it empowered African Americans to take control of their lives.",
        "startTime": 74086,
        "endTime": 77902,
        "slowStartTime": 111279,
        "slowEndTime": 117078
    },
    {
        "text": "But there's a downside.",
        "startTime": 78256,
        "endTime": 79652,
        "slowStartTime": 117534,
        "slowEndTime": 119703
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, at least half of African American children were being raised by a single parent,...",
        "startTime": 79975,
        "endTime": 85598,
        "slowStartTime": 120112,
        "slowEndTime": 128622
    },
    {
        "text": "...according to the 2005 census data.",
        "startTime": 85901,
        "endTime": 88866,
        "slowStartTime": 129002,
        "slowEndTime": 133524
    },
    {
        "text": "And black unemployment is at 15 and a half percent,...",
        "startTime": 89255,
        "endTime": 92751,
        "slowStartTime": 134032,
        "slowEndTime": 139352
    },
    {
        "text": "...almost double the national average.",
        "startTime": 93101,
        "endTime": 95338,
        "slowStartTime": 139801,
        "slowEndTime": 143232
    },
    {
        "text": "The Civil War itself was a part of the great legacy of slavery in this country...",
        "startTime": 95716,
        "endTime": 102442,
        "slowStartTime": 143724,
        "slowEndTime": 153888
    },
    {
        "text": "...and we still live with that every day.",
        "startTime": 102973,
        "endTime": 105868,
        "slowStartTime": 154609,
        "slowEndTime": 159027
    }
]